---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Home · Astro Example" description="Clean MPA starter with About & Contact">
	<section class="stack">
		<h1>Welcome</h1>
		<p class="muted">
			Built with Astro’s multi-page approach for speed and simplicity—ready to switch to a smooth
			single-page experience later if you ever want.
		</p>

		<!-- Quick value props -->
		<div class="card">
			<h2 style="margin-top:0">What’s here</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>File-based routing:</strong> <code>/</code>, <code>/about</code>, <code>/contact</code></li>
				<li><strong>Shared layout:</strong> consistent header, footer, and meta tags</li>
				<li><strong>Clean styles:</strong> tiny global CSS, accessible focus states</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<!-- Useful links -->
		<div class="card">
			<h2 style="margin-top:0">Quick links</h2>
			<p>
				Learn more about this demo on the <a href="/about">About</a> page, or say hello on
				<a href="/contact">Contact</a>.
			</p>
		</div>

		<!-- Tiny “how to extend” section -->
		<div class="card">
			<h2 style="margin-top:0">Next steps</h2>
			<ol>
				<li>Edit copy in <code>src/pages/about.astro</code> and <code>src/pages/contact.astro</code>.</li>
				<li>Add a new page by creating a file under <code>src/pages/your-page.astro</code>.</li>
				<li>Customize styles in <code>public/styles/global.css</code>.</li>
			</ol>
			<p class="muted" style="margin:0">
				Tip: keep it MPA for stability; experiment with SPA transitions later in a branch.
			</p>
		</div>

		<!-- Small showcase row (no extra CSS: inline grid for convenience) -->
		<div style="display:grid; gap:1rem; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));">
			<div class="card">
				<h3 style="margin-top:0">Performance-first</h3>
				<p>Minimal JavaScript by default. Fast loads, simple deployment.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card">
				<h3 style="margin-top:0">Good bones</h3>
				<p>Shared layout + sane defaults make it easy to grow without clutter.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card">
				<h3 style="margin-top:0">Room to play</h3>
				<p>Flip on client navigation later to explore transitions—no lock-in.</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Tiny code breadcrumb for devs -->
		<div class="card">
			<h2 style="margin-top:0">Project map</h2>
			<pre style="margin:0;"><code>.
├── src/
│   ├── components/
│   │   └── Nav.astro
│   ├── layouts/
│   │   └── BaseLayout.astro
│   └── pages/
│       ├── index.astro   ← you are here
│       ├── about.astro
│       └── contact.astro
└── public/
    └── styles/
        └── global.css
</code></pre>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
